    </div>
</section>
<section class="container-fluid bg-white px-0" id="infoDashBoard">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="dynamicFont mt-5 mb-3 mb-md-5">
        The WeBall administrator dashboard:
      </div>
      <div class="h3 font-weight-bold">
        Action tabs:
      </div>
      <div class="h5 mb-0">
        Four action tabs in the middle of the left sidebar controls what appears in the dashboard.
      </div>
      <div class="h5 mb-0">
        Each tab will enable you to perform a different set of tasks.
      </div>
      <div class="h5 mb-0">
        Read the cards below to learn about each action tab.
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group bg-white form-control p-0 flexWrapButtons mt-3" id="infoCardSelection1" role="group" aria-label="Basic example">
        <% ["Bookings", "Prices", "Hours", "Logos"].each do |buttonID| %>
            <button type="button" class="btn border-dark hover-selected rounded-0"
            data-idRef=<%= "#{buttonID}InfoCard" %>><%= buttonID %></button>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-4">
      <div class="bookings tab" id="BookingsInfoCard">
          <%= image_tag(asset_path("dashBoardTable.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-12 col-md-5") %>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-12 offset-md-1">
              <div class="h3 my-3"><i class="fas fa-th pr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Bookings:</div>
              <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
                <li>Display all current and new bookings.</li>
                <li>Create new casual or regular bookings.</li>
                <li>Create single or double venue bookings or full facility bookings.</li>
                <li>Create a custom event when a booking does not fit into an activity category.</li>
                <li>Delete bookings.</li>
              </ul>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prices tab d-none" id="PricesInfoCard">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path("prices_plans.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-12 col-md-5") %>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12 offset-md-1">
            <div class="h3 my-3"><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign pr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Prices:</div>
            <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
              <li>Add a new activity.</li>
              <li>Set the prices for an activity.</li>
              <li>Match activities with their venues.</li>
              <li>Delete an activity.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hours tab d-none" id="HoursInfoCard">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path("hours_plan.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-12 col-md-5") %>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12 offset-md-1">
            <div class="h3 my-3"><i class="far fa-clock pr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Hours:</div>
            <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
              <li>Set the opening hours of your business.</li>
              <li>Set the peak hours of your business.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="logo tab d-none" id="LogosInfoCard">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path("logo_tab.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-12 col-md-5") %>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12 offset-md-1">
            <div class="h3 my-3"><i class="far fa-image pr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Logos:</div>
            <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
              <li>Upload your business's logo.</li>
              <li>Edit the names of your venues.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="container-fluid bg-white px-0 mb-5" id="infoWidget">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="dynamicFont mt-5 mb-3 mb-md-5">
        The WeBall widget:
      </div>
      <div class="h3 font-weight-bold">
        What is it?
      </div>
      <div class="h5 mb-0">
        The WeBall widget is a stand-alone venue booking application that can be embedded into third-party websites.
      </div>
      <div class="h3 font-weight-bold mt-4">
        Why add the WeBall widget to your site?:
      </div>
      <div class="btn-group bg-white form-control p-0 flexWrapButtons mt-3" id="infoCardSelection2" role="group" aria-label="Basic example">
        <% ["No commissions", "Faster bookings", "Keep visitors on your website", "Lower administration expenses"].each do |buttonID| %>
            <button type="button" class="btn border-dark hover-selected rounded-0"
            data-idRef=<%= "#{buttonID.split(' ').join('_')}" %>><%= buttonID %></button>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-4">
      <div class="tab" id="No_commissions">
          <%= image_tag(asset_path("comparison_rates.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-md-5") %>
          <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1   px-1">
              <div class="h3 my-3">No commissions:</div>
              <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
                <li>WeBall is built on POLipay, an online payment service run by Australia Post.</li>
                <li>POLipay charges one of the lowest commissions on online payments in Australia.</li>
                <li>WeBall does not charge any additional commission on top of POLipay, only a flat monthly fee.</li>
              </ul>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tab d-none" id="Faster_bookings">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path("review_page.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-md-5") %>
        <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1   px-1">
            <div class="h3 my-3">Faster bookings:</div>
            <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
              <li>Average online form abandomment rate is 68%.</li>
              <li>The WeBall widget lets customers book faster without account registration.</li>
              <li>Shorter booking times mean less abandonment; less abandonment means more bookings.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tab d-none" id="Keep_visitors_on_your_website">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path("compareSkedda.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-md-5") %>
        <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1   px-1">
            <div class="h3 my-3">Keep visitors on your website:</div>
            <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
              <li>Most booking platforms redirect your internet traffic to their own website.</li>
              <li>This prevents visitors from browsing your other services or products and reduces their exposure to your special offers.</li>
              <li>By embedding the WeBall widget directly into your own website, customers can stay on your website when they book.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tab d-none" id="Lower_administration_expenses">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path("repeatSpeechLg.png"), class: "img-fluid p-0 p-md-4 col-md-5") %>
        <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1   px-1">
            <div class="h3 my-3">Lower administration expenses:</div>
            <ul class="h5 align-left list-dots-mb-3">
              <li>Answering calls on office availability is an inefficient use of staff time.</li>
              <li>WeBall widget lets your customers check office availability in real-time online without the need for staff.</li>
              <li>New bookings appear in real-time on your dashboard</li>
              <li>Reduce time spent on administration with WeBall and save money.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>
